    {195, kDeckId, "circulate", "['sɝkjəlet]", "v. (使)循环；(使)流通；传播；流传；循环；流通", "1. Swimming helps to get the blood circulating through the muscles.\n   游泳有助于肌肉的血液循环。\n2. Ceiling fans circulated warm air around the room.\n   吊扇使暖空气在房间里循环。", ""},
    {196, kDeckId, "circumference", "[sɚ'kʌmfərəns]", "n. 圆周；周围；周长；胸围", "1. a scientist calculating the Earth's circumference.\n   …一位正在计算地球周长的科学家。", ""},
