    {202, kDeckId, "close", "[kloz]", "v&n. 关；结束\na&ad. 近的(地)；紧密的(地)", "1. Let me do the car door – it won't close properly.\n   我来修一下车门，它关不紧。\n2. Would you mind if I closed the window?\n   我把窗户关上你不介意吧？", ""},
