    {207, kDeckId, "include", "[ɪn'klud]", "v. 包括；包含；计入", "1. His job includes looking after under-21 teams.\n   他的职责包括照管21岁以下球队。\n2. The curriculum includes courses in computing.\n   课程内容包括计算机技术。", ""},
