    {277, kDeckId, "mercury", "['mɜːkjəri]", "n. 水银；汞；[化]汞；【天】", "1. Some thieves have eaten off their irons with mercury water.\n   有些窃贼用汞水腐蚀他们的镣铐。\n2. He said that all metals were composed of mercury and sulphur in different proportions .\n   他说一切金属都是由水银和硫黄按不同比例构成的。", ""},
