    {363, kDeckId, "magnificent", "[mæg'nɪfəsnt]", "adj. 华丽的；高尚的；宏伟的；壮丽的", "1. The twelve-mile coastline has magnificent sce-nery.\n   这12英里的海岸线景色壮观。\n2. She looked magnificent in a long red dress.\n   她穿着红色长裙，看起来美极了。", ""},
