    {406, kDeckId, "inform", "[ɪn'fɔrm]", "v. (of；about)通知；告诉；报告；告发；告密；通知", "1. They would inform him of any progress they had made.\n   他们将把自己所取得的任何进展都告诉他。\n2. My daughter informed me that she was pregnant.\n   我女儿告诉我她怀孕了。", ""},
