    {411, kDeckId, "reform", "[rɪ'fɔrm]", "v&n. 改革；改造；改良\nn. /", "1. The party embarked on a programme of economic reform.\n   这个政党开始了一个经济改革的计划。\n2. plans to radically reform the tax system\n   彻底改革税收制度的计划", ""},
