    {443, kDeckId, "diagnose", "[,daɪəɡ'nos]", "v. 诊断(疾病)；判断(问题)；诊断；断定", "1. You can also diagnose your weaknesses with this simple exercise.\n   这样的简单练习还可以诊断你的缺点。\n2. He could diagnose an engine problem simply by listening.\n   他仅靠听就能判断发动机出了什么问题。", ""},
