    {477, kDeckId, "hers", "[hɝz]", "pron. [she的物主代词]她的(所有物)", "1. These are my gloves. Hers are in the drawer.\n   这是我的手套，她的在抽屉里。\n2. He bent and touched his mouth to hers.\n   他俯身吻她的嘴唇。", ""},
