    {485, kDeckId, "hesitate", "['hɛzɪtet]", "v. 犹豫；踌躇；含糊；支吾；不愿", "1. Some parents hesitate to take these steps because they suspect that their child is exaggerating.\n   一些家长迟迟不肯采取这些措施，因为他们怀疑自己的孩子在夸大其词。\n2. I hesitate.\n   我犹豫。", ""},
    {486, kDeckId, "eject", "[ɪ'dʒɛkt]", "v. 喷射；排出；驱逐；逐出；驱逐 A", "1. Two engines cut out and the plane started to eject fuel as it lost height.\n   两个发动机突然熄火，飞机在下降的同时开始喷出燃料。", ""},
