    {739, kDeckId, "move", "[muv]", "v. 移动；迁移；活动；感动\nn. 移动；活动；行动", "1. Please keep the doors closed while the train is moving.\n   火车行驶时请保持车门关闭。\n2. Could you move your car, please? It's blocking the road.\n   你能把车挪一下吗？挡着路了。", ""},
