    {759, kDeckId, "anonymous", "[ə'nɑnəməs]", "adj. 匿名的；无名的；姓氏不明的；无个性特征的；无特色的", "1. According to one employee, who wishes to remain anonymous , the company engaged in illegal activities.\n   根据一位不愿透露姓名的员工所述，这家公司曾从事非法活动。\n2. the anonymous author of a collection of poems\n   一本诗集的佚名作者", ""},
