    {768, kDeckId, "noun", "[naʊn]", "n. 名词", "1. In \"the black cat\" the adjective \"black\"modifies the noun \"cat\".\n   在\"那只黑猫\"中，形容词\"黑的\"修饰名词\"猫\"。\n2. An adjective must agree with its noun in mumber and case.\n   形容词在数和格方面必须符合其所修饰的名词。", ""},
