    {1168, kDeckId, "temptation", "[tɛmp'teʃən]", "n. 引诱；诱惑；诱惑物", "1. Resist the temptation to buy the item until you're certain you need it.\n   要抵挡住购买的诱惑，除非你确有需要。\n2. I finally gave in to the temptation and had a cigarette.\n   我最终还是屈从诱惑，抽了一支烟。", ""},
