    {1212, kDeckId, "evaluate", "[ɪ'væljʊ'et]", "v. 估价；评价；求…的值", "1. We need to evaluate the success of the campaign.\n   我们要评估一下这次运动是否成功。\n2. It can be difficult to evaluate the effectiveness of different treatments.\n   要对各种治疗方法的效果作出评估会很难。", ""},
