    {1234, kDeckId, "inventory", "['ɪnvəntɔri]", "n. 详细目录；存货；财产清册；总量；存货清单；物品清单；库存物品", "1. one inventory of twelve sails for each yacht.\n   …为每艘游艇配备12张帆的存货。", ""},
    {1235, kDeckId, "prevent", "[pri'vɛnt]", "v. (from)预防；防止；阻止；制止；妨碍", "1. Wrap small ornaments in paper to prevent them being damaged.\n   把小饰品用纸包上以免损坏。\n2. The rules are intended to prevent accidents.\n   这些规定旨在预防事故。", ""},
