    {1316, kDeckId, "evident", "['ɛvɪdənt]", "adj. 明显的；明白的", "1. Bob ate his lunch with evident enjoyment.\n   显然鲍勃吃午饭吃得津津有味。", ""},
    {1317, kDeckId, "individual", "[,ɪndɪ'vɪdʒuəl]", "adj. 个人的；单独的；独特的；个别的；独特的 <\nn. 个人；个体", "1. Each individual leaf on the tree is different.\n   树上每片叶子都不相同。\n2. the needs of the individual customer\n   每位顾客的需求", ""},
