    {1319, kDeckId, "provided", "[prə'vaɪdɪd]", "conj. 倘若；只要；假如；假如 <", "1. He can come with us, provided he pays for his own meals.\n   只要他付自己的饭钱，就可以跟我们一起来。", ""},
