    {1343, kDeckId, "science", "['saɪəns]", "n. 科学；技术；学科；理科", "1. Many leading scientists do not consider that science can give absolutely reliable knowledge.\n   许多杰出科学家都不认为科学能够提供绝对可靠的知识。\n2. the founder of modern science, Isaac Newton\n   现代科学创始人艾萨克·牛顿", ""},
