    {1352, kDeckId, "search", "[sɝtʃ]", "v. 搜寻；调查；探求\nn. 搜寻；探究；查究", "1. I've searched high and low for my glasses.\n   我到处找我的眼镜。\n2. It was too dark to search further.\n   天太暗，无法继续寻找。", ""},
