    {1354, kDeckId, "require", "[rɪ'kwaɪr]", "v. 需要；要求；命令", "1. What's required is a complete reorganization of the system.\n   需要做的是彻底整顿整个系统。\n2. Campbell's broken leg will probably require surgery.\n   坎贝尔的一条腿骨折，可能需要手术。", ""},
    {1355, kDeckId, "scientific", "[,saɪən'tɪfɪk]", "adj. 科学的；系统的", "1. We believe in investing in scientific research.\n   我们相信科学研究的投资价值。\n2. decisions based on scientific evidence\n   根据科学证据作出的决定", ""},
    {1356, kDeckId, "attention", "[ə'tɛnʃən]", "n. 注意力；关心；立正！（口令）", "1. Now he's gone, I can give you my undivided attention .\n   现在他已经走了，我可以把全部注意力都放在你身上。\n2. During the lecture Sarah's attention began to wander .\n   上课时，萨拉开始走神了。", ""},
