    {1433, kDeckId, "effort", "['ɛfɚt]", "n. 努力；成就", "1. Church leaders are prepared to meet the terrorists in an effort to find peace.\n   为寻求和平，教会领袖准备与恐怖分子会面。\n2. please make an effort to be polite.\n   请尽量礼貌些。", ""},
