    {1476, kDeckId, "growth", "[ɡroθ]", "n. 增长；发展；生长；种植", "1. The company is preparing for zero growth this year.\n   公司今年准备面对零增长。\n2. measures to stimulate economic growth\n   刺激经济增长的措施", ""},
