    {2288, kDeckId, "disaster", "[dɪ'zæstɚ]", "n. 灾难；灾祸；不幸；天灾", "1. One hundred and twenty people died in China's worst air disaster .\n   有120人在中国这起最惨烈的空难事故中丧生。\n2. Disaster struckwhen two men were killed during their parachute jumps.\n   灾难突然降临，两名男子在跳伞过程中丧生。", ""},
