    {3730, kDeckId, "meadow", "['mɛdo]", "n. 草地；牧场", "1. There are many lambs capering in the meadow.\n   很多小羊在草地上蹦蹦跳跳。\n2. The colt bounded through the meadow.\n   那匹马驹跳着跑过牧场。", ""},
