    {3732, kDeckId, "aluminum", "[ə'lʊmɪnəm]", "n. 铝", "1. He had a house there and a dock and a little aluminum boat.\n   他在那儿有一所房子、一个泊船的码头和一艘小铝船。\n2. And she sat and sat on that aluminum throne ever since.\n   自那以后，她就一直坐在那个铝制的宝座上。", ""},
