    {3734, kDeckId, "normalization", "[nɔrmləˈzeʃən]", "n. 正常化；标准化；正规化；常态化", "1. The trend of half permanent enterprise management culture towards normalization direction.\n   趋势三半永久企业的经营管理文化将朝正规化方向发展。\n2. Our normalization is such that the curves in Fig . 3 can be regarded as probability distributions.\n   我们的标准化处理使得图3中的曲线可以被看作概率分布曲线。", ""},
