    {3742, kDeckId, "outskirts", "['aʊt'skɝts]", "n. 市郊；郊区", "1. On the extreme northwestern outskirts of the city stands the Buddhist temple.\n   那所佛教寺院位于市郊的最西北角。\n2. Why not escape city noises and enter the peace of outskirts with our weekend trip?\n   为什么不参加我们的周末旅行，走出城市的喧闹，步入郊外的宁静呢？", ""},
