    {4188, kDeckId, "earthquake", "['ɝθ'kwek]", "n. 地震；大动荡", "1. An earthquake measuring 6.1 on the Richter scale struck southern California on June 28.\n   6月28日加州南部地区发生了里氏6.1级地震。\n2. The city is in an earthquake zone.\n   该市位于地震带。", ""},
