    {4860, kDeckId, "challenge", "['tʃælɪndʒ]", "n. 挑战；艰巨任务\nv. 向…挑战", "1. They threw down the challenge that he couldn't wash 40 cars in one hour .\n   他们激将他，说他不可能在1小时内擦洗40辆汽车。", ""},
