    {4872, kDeckId, "analyze", "['ænə,laɪz]", "v. 分析；分解", "1. We have to analyze and solve problems.\n   我们要分析问题，解决问题。\n2. We should analyze the causes of failure.\n   我们应该分析一下失败的缘由。", ""},
